{
  "texts": [
    "No significant difference was observed based on the risk of bias (p = 0.77) or based on publication status (p = 0.58).",
    "We assessed publication bias by using a regression analysis to quantify funnel plot asymmetry (Appendix Figures S1 [online]), and it suggested a risk of publication bias (p = 0.027).",
    "In this systematic review and meta-analysis, we analyzed the diagnostic performance of generative AI and physicians.",
    "We initially identified 13,966 studies, ultimately including 54 in the meta-analysis.",
    "The study spanned various AI models and medical specialties, with GPT-4 being the most evaluated."
  ]
}